{"tid":2240183,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黃之鋒：解密鹽田！踢爆鹽田執法人員名單】","createTime":"2020-10-12T13:12:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T02:02:41.000Z","uid":35021,"like":74,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"b0f2d151b247c9b6b4709b3295bd6530f8df9114","tid":2240183,"uid":35021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T13:12:11.000Z","msg":"【解密鹽田！踢爆鹽田執法人員名單】 (全文無需登入付費)<br />\n<br />\n我已掌握鹽田看守所執法人員，以及公安局涉事人員的部份名單。經過連日資料蒐集，現將執法人員的姓名、照片和聯絡方式全數公開。<br />\n對於十二手足被秘密扣押五十日，極有可能遭到嚴刑烤問和逼供，至今仍是音訊全無，家屬委派律師仍未能與當事人會面，他們必然需要負上全責。<br />\n由於事件涉及重大公眾利益，所以即使以Patreon平台發佈，亦不會有任何付費牆的限制，惟明查暗訪的偵查工作實在需要資源，還望各位訂閱支持。<br />\n即使承受國安處追究的風險，與夥伴們花上不少時間精力，方能公開這份名單，但我仍盼望鍥而不捨的，繼續在公共領域貢獻己身，當我們距離中共設局送中的真相越來越近，更不能就此停步。<br />\n「真相是我們的唯一武器」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/posts/42663730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fposts%2F42663730&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2V8%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=28f159da\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/posts/42663730</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BycXQ6B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBycXQ6B.jpg&h=35fce2cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MJ4bVyf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMJ4bVyf.jpg&h=c536ccc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OeBhQ6z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOeBhQ6z.jpg&h=516d19f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oTGYAyd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoTGYAyd.jpg&h=7815d86f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f9bBndd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff9bBndd.jpg&h=71008f13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02ba4b5710b52aef4b5d08828f1a6a7c6201d8a7","tid":2240183,"uid":352936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T13:12:54.0